title: OpenTable CEO on 2026 Dining Trends
description: Debby Soo, OpenTable CEO, says consumers continue to prioritize dining out and the overall restaurant experience. She speaks with Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close.” (Source: Bloomberg)
